    "collapsible_content_YtUiTc": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_wMDRww": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Advanced Smell Proof Technology",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our products are designed with cutting edge filtration systems that help contain and neutralize odors effectively. Using multi layer construction and carbon based filtering, Revelry gear ensures that your items remain discreetly stored anytime, anywhere.</p><p>Whether you're commuting, traveling, or storing personal items at home, you can rely on our smell proof technology to maintain privacy and confidence.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_AxfDkc": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Water Resistant & Weather Ready",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Life doesn’t stop for the weather and neither should your gear.</p><p>Our bags and storage solutions are made with high quality, water resistant materials that help protect your belongings from unexpected spills, rain, and outdoor conditions. From urban environments to rugged adventures, Revelry Supply gear is built to perform.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_JrzE4C": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Built for Durability",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Every product is crafted with premium materials and reinforced construction to ensure long lasting performance. Strong zippers, durable fabrics, and meticulous stitching come together to create gear that stands up to daily use.</p><p>This isn’t just storage, it’s an investment in reliability.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_4zdWEN": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Discreet by Design",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We believe functionality should never compromise style.</p><p>Our designs are intentionally subtle and modern, allowing you to carry your essentials without drawing attention. Whether you're in a professional setting, traveling, or exploring the outdoors, Revelry gear blends seamlessly into your environment.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
