          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/revelry_flatlay_explorer_green.webp",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "Engineered for Every Lifestyle",
            "text": "<p>Revelry Supply isn’t just about products, it’s about enhancing the way you move through your day.</p><ul><li><strong>For Daily Carry: </strong>Stay organized with compact and efficient storage solutions designed to fit effortlessly into your routine.</li><li><strong>For Travel:  </strong>Our spacious and durable gear ensures your essentials stay protected, whether you're heading out for a weekend trip or a longer journey.</li><li><strong>For Storage: </strong>Keep your items secure at home with smell proof and protective solutions that offer peace of mind.</li><li><strong>For Adventure:</strong>From city streets to outdoor escapes, Revelry gear is built to keep up with your lifestyle.</li></ul>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_a3N3XM": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
