            "caption": "",
            "heading": "Smarter Storage Starts Here",
            "text": "<p>Not all bags are created equal.</p><p>Traditional bags may offer storage but they don’t provide protection, discretion, or durability. Revelry Supply takes storage to the next level by combining innovative technology with practical design.</p><p><strong>Our smell proof gear is engineered to help:</strong></p><ul><li>Contain and minimize odors</li><li>Protect contents from moisture</li><li>Keep items organized and secure</li><li>Maintain discretion in any environment</li></ul><p>This is storage redefined for modern needs.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_hFzRi7": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Revelry-LayeredTechGraphicDEFENDER_c44c9a47-9bb7-409e-b324-fb3d2e3bc7f8.jpg",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "Customer Focused Design",
            "text": "<p>Everything we create starts with you.</p><p>We design products based on real world use of what you actually need in your everyday life. From intuitive compartments to ergonomic designs, every detail is carefully considered to improve usability and comfort.</p><p>Our goal is simple: to make your life easier, more organized, and more secure.</p>",
